{"about_the_game":"<strong><i>\u201cStay still and I will reach you. Run and I will still reach you. I am outside of your door and beyond every horizon. You will remember who I am and you will come to me.\u201d</i></strong><br><br><i>Each night point-and-click Aggy through Somnipathy - a creepy and surreal dungeon crawling thriller -while utilizing each day to prepare. If you fail, there\u2019s always tomorrow\u2026 right?</i><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2069260/extras/SurviveAggy.gif?t=1715118935\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><i>When I\u2019m at work and when I\u2019m at rest, it watches my every move. I need your help to survive this. They.  Are. Everywhere\u2026</i></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Use every day to prepare for the night. Go to your job, talk to people, buy gear, and explore the world you take for granted<br></li><li>Every night the enemy returns - avoid monsters, solve puzzles, and go a little further than the night before</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2069260/extras/PursueCreep2.gif?t=1715118935\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><i>I feel like I could collapse at any moment\u2026do I have what it takes to be relentless? By day, I must prepare. Guide me to solve these doubts that bind me.</i></h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Outsmart your pursuer - tireless and relentless, you'll need every trick in the book to defeat them<br></li><li>Tackle strange and vicious bosses, whose forms defy reality</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2069260/extras/ConnectLamp2.gif?t=1715118935\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><i>I know I can\u2019t be the only one yearning to do more with life. Though I feel invisible at work and uncertain of tomorrow, who else is out there? Help me gain strength to endure these obstacles.</i></h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Make connections with those around you, no matter how monstrous they seem<br></li><li>Play Score attack mode. How long can you withstand sleeplessness? Be the very best... In. The. World!<br></li><li>Dive into the twisted world of Somnipathy</li></ul><br>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Ska Net","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2069260/b5a0b2d33355bc019c50d6b88309df513a3703fd.jpg"},{"name":"Dead End","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2069260/1e7f808ec7fbc502c7a6f3ace4ddb73ecb1c55db.jpg"},{"name":"Pointed and Clicked!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2069260/9dcbe59e661071abe83ccaf50a3adb87018ad100.jpg"},{"name":"Clicked and Pointed!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2069260/bb4de20c7db866f714b904c95a97cf17e3b32af8.jpg"},{"name":"Sunderland Memorial Award","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2069260/331585ed148c37f06ce3c04bc5c9c3c365ec68fa.jpg"},{"name":"Laundry?","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2069260/e72d3a97b3b4832fcfd0072af90e50532e684460.jpg"},{"name":"Sleep Paralysis","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2069260/bd74bacbea310740e548c965431c5585f8582a68.jpg"},{"name":"Restless Leg Syndrome","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2069260/c3976f8395d159d0587efd1e25fe54c018444c73.jpg"},{"name":"Bruxism","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2069260/88da5ef0b01a6492046de52008ba94b7e709c640.jpg"},{"name":"Somnia","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2069260/27af938bfe8f33e35a3b2a073252399961a928f6.jpg"}],"total":40},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2069260/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1715118935","background_raw":"https